- [ ] **Create DarkModeToggle component**

- [ ] **Make everything mobile-first responsive** (test on ≤480px)

- [ ] **Replace all icons with Lucide React icons**

- [ ] **Add loading skeletons/spinners** wherever data is fetched

- [ ] **Add toast notifications**  
      Use `react-hot-toast` for success/error messages.

