You now have a complete, fully local, TypeScript-based roadmap using Next.js App Router, raw PostgreSQL, local file storage, and NextAuth for authentication.

No external services required – everything runs on your machine.

Go build MochiDo and blow your supervisor away with that emotional hamster magic! 🐹✨
